    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver or a fun weekend cruiser. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner today! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
