      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-spec BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a factory Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to maintain variable valve timing precision. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings to preserve the communicative steering rack feel. Minor aesthetic imperfections exist, but the mechanical integrity is robust, with a cooling system overhaul and rod bearing inspection already completed. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 37500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
